extends ../../layout

block style
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/lib/swiper/css/swiper.min.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/css/my.swiper.css')
block content
  include ../../component/navbar.pug
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-3
        include ../component/menu.pug
      .col-md-9
        h2 speed
        p 滑动速度，即slider自动滑动开始到结束的时间(单位ms)，也是触摸滑动时释放至贴合的时间。
        h4 speed参数
        p 类型：<span class="label label-info">number</span> 默认：<span class="label label-info">300</span> 举例：<span class="label label-info">2000</span> 启用版本：<span class="label label-info">3.0.0</span>
        h4 效果演示
        .desc
          .swiper-container#e1
            .swiper-wrapper
              .swiper-slide slider1
              .swiper-slide slider2
              .swiper-slide slider3
          p
            span.label.label-danger 300
          .swiper-container#e2
            .swiper-wrapper
              .swiper-slide slider1
              .swiper-slide slider2
              .swiper-slide slider3
          p
            span.label.label-danger 2000
          .alert.alert-info 小技巧：利用transition-timing-sunction改变Swiper的切换时间曲线
          .swiper-container#e3
            .swiper-wrapper.my-ania
              .swiper-slide slider1
              .swiper-slide slider2
              .swiper-slide slider3
          p
            span.label.label-danger 2000
block script
  script(src="/lib/swiper/js/swiper.jquery.min.js")
  script(src="/js/my.swiper.js")
  script.
    $(function() {
      var my_1 = new Swiper('#e1', {
        autoplay: 3000,
        speed: 300,
      })
      var my_2 = new Swiper('#e2', {
        autoplay: 3000,
        speed: 2000,
      })
      var my_3 = new Swiper('#e3', {
        autoplay: 3000,
        speed: 2000,
      })
    })